      "html": "<aside class=\"sidenote\" id=\"letter-372-page-1-sidenote-1\" data-letter=\"372\" data-page=\"1\" data-pos=\"left\" data-annotation=\"am linken Rand\">\n   <div class=\"lb-line-block\" data-type=\"break\"><span class=\"fn\" data-index=\"3\"><span class=\"anchor\">☓</span></span>Graf Solmes General Berg u. s. w. auch die Igelströhms</div>\n</aside>"
