      "html": "<aside class=\"sidenote\" id=\"letter-372-page-4-sidenote-1\" data-letter=\"372\" data-page=\"4\" data-pos=\"left\" data-annotation=\"am linken Rand, vertikal\">\n   <div class=\"lb-line-block\" data-type=\"break\">In der Woche der hoffentlichen Eröfnung eines <span class=\"aq\">depot de litterature.</span></div>\n</aside>"
    }
  ]
